8, 4802 Ebensee','ATU69080326','餐廳','这家餐馆是由自助餐以及铁板烧模式组合而成的亚洲风餐饮，口味是稍微偏向欧洲式的。我们当然还可以让客人点菜单上的菜品，但我主要卖的是自主餐加铁板烧还有好吃好看的甜点！\n每人平均只要30欧（包含饮料）让您们吃到饱腹。只是每周一我们歇息！\n热烈欢迎大家关顾！！?','xuxiaoqing1965@gmail.com','+4369911621159','www.asia-dao.at','+43681 81100860','susi069911621159','+436706076383',NULL,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/qZtgRzTLrvqmTrBxwytx.png','[\"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/3QsN3ZSRQqQ0uoKiBb8m.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/rs6VVcMzEdiFlOALYVQG.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/veiXmmYNd1PG02aIjtdC.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/nqWv8I7fMwwYQku0JHsh.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260609/IVpZBh9gP6a4BDx4d9EX.png\"]',1,NULL,'2026-06-10 22:49:56',0,1,'2026-06-09 12:33:30','2026-06-10 22:49:56');


