pan@gmx.net','Gasgasse 4/2/20, A-1150 Vienna',NULL,'LouisPan168','00436603161565','00436603161565','[\"中文\", \"English\", \"德語(Deutsch)\"]','2009','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\", \"Travel agency\"]',1,NULL,'Austria certified guide\nGTG Guide App CEO\nViaAsia Travel Agency CEO','Louis Pan',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260228/O7oO8c9Rl0ZXCK17q1Zu.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260228/b4TnuCHcgnbS3D9YeYtO.png',NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-02-28 11:10:10','2026-02-28 22:23:07'),(33,16,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260302/BiC5LNJiPs2z08jxKUF4.png','曹雪娇','Xuejiao Cao','+436607635268','caoxvejiao@gmail.com','Au 93, 4822 Bad Goisern am Hallstättsee','个人网站：https://cguide.at/impressum/','+436607635268','+436607635268','同上','[\"中文\"]','2022','[\"Local guide\"]',1,NULL,'我是來自薩爾茨卡默古特（Salzkammergut）地區的政府認證導遊，提供德語及中文的專業導覽，以及半日遊與一日遊行程。\n作為一名奧地利官方認證的中文導遊，我已成功通過奧地利聯邦商會（WKO）的國家級培訓與考試，並持有官方頒發的導遊證。我以可靠且專業的態度，帶領賓客深度探索薩爾茨堡（Salzburg）、薩爾茨卡默古特地區，以及哈修塔特（Hallstatt）、巴德伊舍（Bad Ischl）與聖沃夫岡（St. Wolfgang）。','曹雪娇',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260302/PP5rG0maOc7t5ZNtDXJE.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-03-02 10:36:22','2026-03-02 10:36:42'),(34,15,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260301/69e0xaVuIkJxeI2U7qZM.png','Lumo','Lumo','+436605646969','support@lumoguide.com','Salzburg',NULL,'+436605646969',NULL,NULL,'[\"中文\"]','2026','[\"Other\"]',5,'Customer Service','為大家服務','Lumo',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260301/bTRPRYvP7RZQhQpQgrod.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-03-03 09:51:45','2026-03-03 10:05:11'),(35,17,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260305/n5hAIiX3GByv1zxbSBYZ.png','Ruby','Ruby','+436606707757','ydbonnie@hotmail.com','Beijing',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"English\"]','2008','[\"Local guide\"]',1,NULL,'Local Guide','Ruby',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260305/TsWyu3ZPq2tI29TZst77.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-03-05 08:07:00','2026-03-05 08:07:30'),(36,8,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20251123/8r40HOjiymiCCBe52P3L.png','Sunny Bridge GmbH','Helen','+4915737658778','info@come2eu.net','Bayrischzeller Str. 4, 83714 Miesbach','helen0092',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"中文\", \"德語(Deutsch)\"]','2012','[\"Travel agency\"]',4,NULL,'欧洲地接社','琪',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20251123/gWnUx1aI1APJVSvbA26o.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-03-05 12:04:30','2026-03-05 22:49:27'),(37,21,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260316/3jPr7kyIH0JMlluIm2td.png','盛开','SHENG KAI','+41798151679','shengkaich@hotmail.com','Brüggmoosstrasse 2a, 4513 Langendorf Switzerland',NULL,'CH0041798151679','0041798151679','0041798151679','[\"中文\", \"English\"]','1992','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\"]',2,NULL,'专业导游，持有瑞士合法车辆运营资质（121），合法客运车辆，商业乘客保险。可以承接全瑞士境内导游兼司机服务。','盛开',1,'Mercedez benz, V-Class 八座车',0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260316/r2Nbamuwvz1GnnPjKEUY.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260316/I0RVyP6MsE4jT9k7Tlc0.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260316/WpQI73O40gXoVpAGqwRq.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260316/5cbc4e0o9gqq7DyzyPqQ.png','[\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260316\\/EAhwTi1OyA21HUuu5DFW.png\",\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260316\\/qqMmGlfYI4mEks6aikg7.png\"]',1,NULL,'2026-03-16 05:20:47','2026-03-16 05:26:17'),(38,22,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/DK44PLKan8pLnPVUyfVl.png','廖容','Rong LIAO','+436764178855','rong.liao@outlook.at','Rudolf Staudinger Straße 2, Schwanenstadt 4690',NULL,'JWR968','06764178855',NULL,'[\"中文\", \"English\", \"德語(Deutsch)\"]','2025','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\"]',1,NULL,'我是一名深耕于上奥地利州的官方认证导游，主要服务区域涵盖 Linz 及周边，以及 Salzkammergut（包括 Hallstatt、St. Wolfgang、Bad Ischl 等经典旅游目的地）。\n\n熟练掌握中文、英文与德文，能够为不同背景的客人提供专业、流畅且富有深度的讲解与沟通。\n\n同时，我经营本地出租车公司并持有出租车驾驶执照，可提供 Vienna、Salzburg、Linz 与湖区之间的接送服务。\n\n服务涵盖：\n• 私人定制旅行与深度讲解\n• 一日/多日包车行程\n• 商务接待与机场接送','廖容',1,'五座车 1 辆\n七座车 1 辆\n八座车 1 辆',0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/5b7BDlJUtyzkSkRggPT6.png',NULL,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/mGTLb57xe4pKIq9Au7Qm.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/hmIsEnrf0MQzr1xjihMs.png','[\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260318\\/fP1RxYzFu0w3CPegq15z.png\",\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260318\\/VsbELGAypQIUJDIChry2.png\",\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260318\\/h2gnxvqnZYjpeHHbcel9.png\",\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260318\\/5GjzKhVyjOhZccxIRraR.png\",\"https:\\/\\/api.lumoguide.com\\/storage\\/uploads\\/20260318\\/IqGUobVfkmGorv3TJnOk.png\"]',1,NULL,'2026-03-18 04:22:58','2026-03-18 04:39:47');


