及⾹港、\n台湾等华语旅游团队。 通过本⼈专业的旅游知识和热情的接待服务， 为客户在欧洲期间留下\n美好的回忆!','Wendy',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260124/c2X707jmkveP3dIqoogw.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260124/BB9VEc6VzKUAiV7Puyiw.png',NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-01-24 07:30:51',0,1,3,1,'2026-01-24 06:58:26','2026-02-28 05:54:08'),(12,29,7,2,29,'布達佩斯','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260124/rqbgJ5SccLB2VKXtuxnK.png','耿净','Jane','+36704559576','geng_263@hotmail.com','1144 Budapest Ond vezer utja 17/d 8',NULL,'1327136746',NULL,NULL,'[\"中文\", \"English\", \"匈牙利語（Magyar）\"]','2012','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\"]',1,NULL,'本人自 2012 年至今从事专业导游工作，持有匈牙利导游资\n格证书。擅长匈牙利、奥地利、捷克、斯洛伐克、波兰等欧洲\n国家线路。有丰富的带团经验，包括大型旅游团、政府考察及\n公务团等。熟练掌握欧洲各国历史，国家概况及景点讲解。\n性格开朗大方，有较好的亲和力，且有较强的应变能力，对\n各种突发事件能做到妥善处理。能与同事及客户协调好关系，\n具有良好的团队合作精神。','Jane',0,NULL,0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260124/LRdT7AnmrN1DLO4WVKb6.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260124/vxXH0KMUZJYLWGPn2zru.png',NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-01-24 08:58:05',0,1,2,1,'2026-01-24 08:56:56','2026-02-28 05:54:02'),(13,32,34,2,29,'維也納','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260220/55s3GOcZEwGFHM4unpSp.png','田豐豐','Fengfeng Tian','+4369910191884','fengfengtian@msn.com','Kammelweg 1，1210，Vienna',NULL,'fengfengtian','+4369910191884','fengfengtian','[\"中文\", \"English\", \"德語(Deutsch)\", \"法語(Français)\"]','2010','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\"]',1,NULL,'专业欧洲导游领队','Fengfeng',0,NULL,1,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260220/dkLHvyNGadjMxnamUE4D.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[]',1,NULL,'2026-02-20 08:51:33',0,1,0,1,'2026-02-20 08:38:49','2026-04-09 02:49:00'),(14,37,34,2,29,'維也納','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260228/Vw3YAdJjEteT3YecJBn9.png','潘羽筑','Yuchu Pan','+436603161565','louispan@gmx.net','Gasgasse 4/2/20, A-1150 Vienna',NULL,'LouisPan168','00436603161565','00436603161565','[\"中文\", \"English\", \"德語(Deutsch)\"]','2009','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\", \"Trav