e.com/storage/uploads/20260318/DK44PLKan8pLnPVUyfVl.png','廖容','Rong LIAO','+436764178855','rong.liao@outlook.at','Rudolf Staudinger Straße 2, Schwanenstadt 4690',NULL,'JWR968','06764178855',NULL,'[\"中文\", \"English\", \"德語(Deutsch)\"]','2025','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\"]',1,NULL,'我是一名深耕于上奥地利州的官方认证导游，主要服务区域涵盖 Linz 及周边，以及 Salzkammergut（包括 Hallstatt、St. Wolfgang、Bad Ischl 等经典旅游目的地）。\n\n熟练掌握中文、英文与德文，能够为不同背景的客人提供专业、流畅且富有深度的讲解与沟通。\n\n同时，我经营本地出租车公司并持有出租车驾驶执照，可提供 Vienna、Salzburg、Linz 与湖区之间的接送服务。\n\n服务涵盖：\n• 私人定制旅行与深度讲解\n• 一日/多日包车行程\n• 商务接待与机场接送','廖容',1,'五座车 1 辆\n七座车 1 辆\n八座车 1 辆',0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/5b7BDlJUtyzkSkRggPT6.png',NULL,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/mGTLb57xe4pKIq9Au7Qm.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/hmIsEnrf0MQzr1xjihMs.png','[\"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/fP1RxYzFu0w3CPegq15z.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/VsbELGAypQIUJDIChry2.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/h2gnxvqnZYjpeHHbcel9.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/5GjzKhVyjOhZccxIRraR.png\", \"https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/IqGUobVfkmGorv3TJnOk.png\"]',1,NULL,'2026-03-18 00:24:44',0,1,1,1,'2026-03-17 19:59:36','2026-06-07 22:38:01'),(23,54,1,2,7,'巴黎','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/jaQ1A8SGyH3GiamR5sMk.png','李苍龙','li/canglong','+33769466788','4317825@qq.com','248 rue du general leclerc 78400 chatou(france)',NULL,'13942020720','+33769466788',NULL,'[\"中文\", \"法語(Français)\"]','2005','[\"Local guide\", \"Tour leader\", \"Driver guide\"]',2,NULL,'主要负责法国一地司兼导，或者整个欧洲导游。熟悉欧洲历史人文，讲解生动直白。情商高，可以服务任何类型团队','李苍龙',1,'奔驰八座商务',0,'https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/IBCGlVUdHYyJW6Yyesyj.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/pdySU7qnHFOuQm4w0MxH.png','https://api.lumoguide.com/storage/uploads/20260318/Kt0BB2Y5yRQO5VzB08Gq.png','https://api.lumoguide.